Validate RTE Results and Generate Warnings

Source: R/calc_rte.R
validate_rte_results.Rd

Validate RTE Results and Generate Warnings

Usage

validate_rte_results(results, min_loset_warning, quiet)

Arguments

results

Combined unit and overall results

min_loset_warning

Least number of LOSET cases that should exist or the function will warn.

Value

Logical indicating if non-normality was detected in any unit

Details

Performs validation checks on calculated results:

  • Low LOSET counts

  • Units with too few valid RTE measurements

  • Potential non-normal distributions
